examples.problem:
For each of the following pairs, indicate which one of the two species is larger:
(a) $\mathrm{N}^{3-}$ or $\mathrm{F}^{-}$;
(b) $\mathrm{Mg}^{2+}$ or $\mathrm{Ca}^{2+}$;
(c) $\mathrm{Fe}^{2+}$ or $\mathrm{Fe}^{3+}$

Predict which element of the following pairs will have the higher density and support your prediction using periodic trends :
(a) Cr or W ;
(b) W or Os;
(c) Pd or Ag ; and
(d) Y or Nb .
